# Belt-and-suspenders. The image build context is ./portal (see portal/Dockerfile
# + CI), so these repo-root dirs are already outside it and can't be sent to the
# daemon. This file only takes effect if the build context is ever the repo root —
# in that case, keep local per-agent tooling, dev/CI material, design sources, and
# VCS metadata out of the image.
.git
.claude/
.codex/
.gemini/
.agent/
dev/
infra/
onlytty
*.tar
